## Limitations

This report is based on available data up to October 2023 and the specific search results provided. The dynamic nature of political and economic situations means that new developments may not be captured. Additionally, the reliance on secondary sources may introduce biases inherent in the original reporting. Further primary research and direct interviews with stakeholders in Cuba would provide a more nuanced understanding of the protests' causes and implications.